<section class="home-index">
  <div class="main">
    <article>

      <div class="hero">
        <p class="tagline">Accept payments simply &amp; easily</p>
        <p class="minorline">The easiest way for Australians to accept payments in a few minutes.</p>
        <p><%= link_to "Sign up • Free", new_user_registration_path, :class => "button" %></p>
        <p class="image-rotation">
          <%= image_tag "new_page_form.png" %>
          <%= image_tag "payment_page.png", :style => "display: none;" %>
          <%= image_tag "payment_analysis.png", :style => "display: none;" %>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="works">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <ul class="first'">
          <li class="step-one first">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="step">Step 1</i>
              <h3>Sign up</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p><%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path %> for a free account with your name, email and a password.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="step-two last">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="step">Step 2</i>
              <h3>Set up a payment page</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>Set up your payment page by entering a few details.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="last">
          <li class="step-three first">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="step">Step 3</i>
              <h3>Connect to Pin</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>Sign up to <%= link_to "Pin Payments", "http://www.pin.net.au", :target => "_blank" %> to grab a live API key and add it to your account.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="step-four last">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="step">Step 4</i>
              <h3>Share and craft</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>Share your page then go back to crafting that amazing thing you were crafting.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="features">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul class="first">
          <li class="first">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="icon-download-alt"></i>
              <h3>Digital Delivery</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>Sell anything, even digital files. We allow you to upload a 10MB file which will be sent to your customers on payment.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="header">
              <i class="icon-lock"></i>
              <h3>Secure and encrypted</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>All our pages are covered under 256-bit SSL encryption making them secure and encrypted.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="last">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="icon-credit-card"></i>
              <h3>Never store credit cards</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>We use Pin Payments to handle all credit card information we receive  so we don't have to.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="last">
          <li class="first">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="icon-desktop"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i class="icon-tablet"></i>&nbsp;<i class="icon-mobile-phone"></i>
              <h3>Looks great everywhere</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>From the smallest phone, to the largest screen, our payment pages will look great. </p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="header">
              <i class="icon-bar-chart"></i>
              <h3>Simple analysis</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>See your sales this week, month and since you created your payment page at a glance.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="last">
            <div class="header">
              <i class="icon-envelope"></i>
              <h3>Automatic emails</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>Receipts and notifications are emailed to you and your customer automatically.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing">
        <h2>Pricing</h2>
        <p>It's free! Unlimited Payment Pages!</p>
        <%= link_to "Sign up • Free", new_user_registration_path, :class => "button" %>
        <p class="pin">Transactions are subject to <%= link_to "Pin Payments", "http://www.pin.net.au", :target => "_blank" %> additional transaction charges of 3% + 30c per transaction.</p>
      </div>


    </article>
  </div>
</section>